<h3 class="was-h6"> <a href="#update-20151204-0110" itemprop="liveBlogUpdate.url"> <time datetime="2015-12-04T01:10:00+00:00" itemprop="liveBlogUpdate.datePublished"></time> <span>01:10</span> </a> </h3>
<h3 class="was-h3" itemprop="liveBlogUpdate.headline">Full result</h3>
<div itemprop="liveBlogUpdate.articleBody">
<p> Jim McMahon (Lab) 17,209 (62.11%, +7.33%) </p>
<p> John Bickley (UKIP) 6,487 (23.41%, +2.80%) </p>
<p> James Daly (C) 2,596 (9.37%, -9.61%) </p>
<p> Jane Brophy (LD) 1,024 (3.70%, +0.01%) </p>
<p> Simeon Hart (Green) 249 (0.90%, -1.05%) </p>
<p> Sir Oink-A-Lot (Loony) 141 (0.51%) </p>
<p> Lab maj 10,722 (38.70%) </p>
<p> 2.27% swing UKIP to Lab </p>
<p> Electorate 69,009; Turnout 27,706 (40.15%, -19.48%) </p>
