<h3 class="was-h3" itemprop="liveBlogUpdate.headline">Is the rain to blame for poor turnout fears?</h3>
<div itemprop="liveBlogUpdate.articleBody">
<p> "It's pouring down with rain in Oldham, which may have an impact on tonight's turnout," reports Laura Hughes. </p>
